ASK_USER=Ask the user with the Ask tool.
SKILLS_DIR=~/.omp/agent/skills
RULES_SOURCE=`AGENTS.md` files in repo scope and global `~/.omp/agent/RULES.md`
PROGRESS_TOOL=todo
FILE_DISCOVERY=Use Glob for patterns, Grep for text, and LSP for symbol-aware navigation. Do not fall back to shell commands unless no dedicated tool is available.
WEB_RESEARCH=Use WebSearch to find information and Read to retrieve specific pages. Prefer official documentation over blog posts.
DISPATCH_RESEARCHER=Use Task with `agent: "scout"` for read-only research. Give it a scoped prompt and collect its result before acting on it.
